      <p class="about-paragraph">Skriftr is a personal project. This website <i> does not collect data, share data, or
          operate as a business in
          any way.</i> And it is totally free! It was created as a personal way to produce a full stack web application,
        while learning along the way.
        <br>
        <br>
        If you'd like to help me, please make an account, explore, and leave feedback!
      </p>
