          information
          can be lost, and systems can break.</i> I do not have the resources to account for every possibility, and do
        not
        want anyone using this application to feel misled. So please, experiment and use this website as much as you'd
        like! But protect yourself by not using a repeat password, use a long password, and never make any journal
        entries
        that include personal information. Thank you.</p>
